%81-ph%C3%B3-H%C3%A0-T%C3%A2y-ph%C3%A1n-quan/poem-pJIF07o2Qkh5pVVW0kebdg">Tống tòng đệ Á phó Hà Tây phán quan - 送從弟亞赴河西判官</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Tu%E1%BA%BF-y%E1%BA%BFn-h%C3%A0nh/poem-93-OV94G2z33TdoBuUwa_A">Tuế yến hành - 歲晏行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Th%C3%A1i/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-t%E1%BB%91-n%E1%BB%AF-%C4%91%E1%BB%93/poem-zKxXLoEGNYomPBDzqeOzqA">Vịnh tố nữ đồ - 詠素女圖</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Th%C3%A1i/author-Hcb43Ci-Tifm0ivlHzUJXg">Phạm Thái</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%C3%A2u-X%E1%BB%A9-C%C6%A1/V%E1%BB%8Dng-B%E1%BB%93ng-Lai-Du-h%E1%BB%A9ng/poem-Uoy2mSjnk7btxI4Fq9Zp3A">Vọng Bồng Lai - Du hứng - 望蓬萊—遊興</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%C3%A2u-X%E1%BB%A9-C%C6%A1/author-Xdrx9PY_HQVilIv5qP5QxQ">Khâu Xứ Cơ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
